channel.title: Port Forwarding, I'm ALMOST done
channel.description:
Okay, I found my default gateway and my Ip address, I followed a tutorial at Portforward.com. Now, I got to this point in the tutorial but I did not understand one bit what it was talking about, it just had 1 sentence and it practically said fill it in.
I don't know what to put in the boxes. I have a linksys router if that's helpful in any way.
